{"tid":2078138,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港仲想食離岸人民幣條水？","createTime":"2020-06-24T20:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T05:11:50.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8772cd2bc09702d76598ff888a8a44ca6991e0c","tid":2078138,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Sh5rHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Sh5rHO.jpg&h=bb6eb62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國與英國之間的人民幣跨境結算也創下新高。截至2019年8月，中英之間的人民幣跨境結算猛增48%至3,770億元人民幣，超過2018年全年結算額。倫敦金融城公司政策主席凱瑟琳&middot;麥吉尼斯（Catherine McGuinness）表示，「倫敦金融城也已經成長為人民幣交易的主要樞紐，通過倫敦的人民幣外匯交易規模遠超其他任何金融中心」。<br />\n<br />\n中國在開放資本市場的過程中第一時間想到的就是香港。然而，嚴重的社會動盪動搖了中國繼續向香港「下注」的決心。人民幣國際化和金融開放關係到中國的發展戰略，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋不能放在一個籃子裏</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80/398798/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%90%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%BF%E9%8C%AF%E5%A4%B1%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AE%258F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580%2F398798%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258B%25BF%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%2587&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfRdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=28f0511a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80/398798/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%90%E9%9B%A2%E